As a user, I want to list product as a user.

20
00:01:20,090 --> 00:01:23,120
I want to filter products as per brand and categories.

21
00:01:23,270 --> 00:01:28,400
As a user, I want to add products to my shopping cart so I can check out later.

22
00:01:28,550 --> 00:01:33,380
As a user, I want to apply a coupon to get a discount and check the total cost.

23
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:38,090
And as a user, I want to checkout my shopping cart and create an order process.

24
00:01:38,210 --> 00:01:43,490
As a user, I want to view my previous orders and order history, items, etc.

25
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:49,460
So I've expanded the user stories of the application that you can see on the slide.

26
00:01:49,490 --> 00:01:53,300
Basically this is just a list of user stories.

27
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:56,600
I've highlighted the verbs and nouns.

28
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:04,790
So you can see that we've marked in red, those are the verbs and marked in black for

29
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:05,540
nouns.

30
00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:12,320
So for example as a user I want to list products, filter products, view products, add products,

31
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,150
