32
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:21,290
By doing this, you can clearly see what we have is interactions and what we have is domains.

33
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:29,330
The black boxes are domains and the red boxes are interactions between the domains.

34
00:02:29,330 --> 00:02:35,900
List products, filter products, view products, add products, buy shopping cart, view items

35
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:38,690
in shopping cart, view items, shopping cart.

36
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:44,240
And we can also calculate and assign billing address and shipping address.

37
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,770
Assign credit card.

38
00:02:45,770 --> 00:02:50,570
Checkout shopping cart and manage stock.

39
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:58,010
Receive order confirmation, email and order number, list orders and order history items, login system

40
00:02:58,010 --> 00:02:59,000
etc.

41
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:05,420
Bây giờ tôi sẽ trích xuất các danh từ và động từ từ các user stories.

42
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:11,180
Bây giờ tôi đang tìm kiếm các danh từ sẽ trở thành các đối tượng chính chứ không phải các thuộc tính.

43
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:17,690
